title: University of Newcastle Students - Newcastle University Anime Club is Looking For You

embed.description: NUAC - Newcastle University Anime Club, Newcastle, New South Wales. 774 likes · 110 talking about this · 26 were here. NUAC is a social group at the...

body: For all the League players from Newcastle, NSW, currently studying at the University of Newcastle our club will be supporting all teams signing up to represent UoN. If you're looking for a team feel free to ask on our Facebook page or you can email nuac.contact@gmail.com and we can try and put you in touch with other players in our area. If you have any questions feel free to ask.
